---
title: BBQ Chicken Burger & Onion Chutney with Kūmara Fries & Mayonnaise
description: Quick juicy chicken seasoned with a barbecue zap is a smokey dream come true for your taste buds. Place it between two buns, serve with vibrant kūmara fries and glaze the chicken with an onion chutney to elevate these burgers to the next level.
